<title>19.9-16.12.2022 Lecture groups BIA and BIB for winter semester of 2022/2023 academic year</title>
<link>https://www.fit.vut.cz/study/study-news/h19068/</link>
<description>The recommended (approximate) division into the lecture groups is as follows:&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;1BIT students with surname beginning with &lt;B&gt;A to N&lt;/B&gt; are in the &lt;B&gt;1BIA group&lt;/B&gt;,
&lt;LI&gt;1BIT students with surname beginning with &lt;B&gt;O to Ž&lt;/B&gt; are in the &lt;B&gt;1BIB group&lt;/B&gt;,
&lt;LI&gt;for students in &lt;B&gt;2BIT&lt;/B&gt;, the groups are recommended based on the summer semester of the 2021/2022 academic year (alphabetically, the middle is approximately between L and M).
&lt;/UL&gt;
If there is room in the lecture rooms, the &lt;B&gt;membership in the groups is not going to be checked&lt;/B&gt;. When the capacity of the lecture room is reached, students that have the second group in schedule collision and then students that are members of the particular group have priority.
&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;
The mid-semester exams are going to be organized separately in the individual courses. You &lt;B&gt;don't have to report&lt;/B&gt; the change of the lecture group due to the schedule collision - just go to the activity that does not have the collision.</description>
